title: Taylor Swift’s 10-Minute Version of All Too Well Almost Wasn’t Recorded (Extended) | Tonight Show
author: The Tonight Show Starring Jimmy Fallon
description:
Taylor Swift talks about the highly anticipated release of RED (Taylor’s Version), including never-heard-before songs, and shares the story of why "All Too Well" is actually 10 minutes long.
